ender the entire output in this exact art style: Hand-drawn pencil sketch with cross-hatching and graphite shading. The clothing and background descriptions above describe subject matter, not rendering technique — they must not override the chosen art style.\\n\\nFINAL REMINDER: Exactly 1 human in the output. No other people. Anything else visible (objects, posters, screens, reflections, background figures) must NOT become a person."
`;

